item.title: Join the Club
item.description: Anyone interested in coding is welcome to attend a programming club meeting. We meet on Tuesdays at 11:00 am in Coover 115 on the PennWest campus. Also join our discord using this link before 2/28/2023: https://discord.gg/Pvv2Eu8FrF
